title: PLUTOSKI

description.plain: “PLUTOSKI”, the fifth track from Future’s mixtape, MIXTAPE PLUTO, is a trap song filled with braggadocios bars. The song became a meme on TikTok upon its release due to its chorus, which features mumble-like vocals.
